It would be helpful if users could create "personal" groups. Like distribution lists in Microsoft Outlook. This way, if they want to perform a filter with a select group of users, they could create a personal group and then filter on that group. Similarly, if they want to share a filter with select users, they could do so by creating a personal group. This solves 2 other issue requests (linked) in an elegant manner.

